metadata.name: Flag #1
metadata.description: The Atlas Lions of Morocco have reached the quarter final of the Qatar 2022 FIFA World Cup. To celebrate this landmark victory, KLDPXL x Edge of Arabia x YallaSwap are dropping a limited collection of 11 digital Moroccan flags artworks, with an elegant mosaic-patterned background. The items are non-transferable until the next World Cup in 2026.
